{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Scleria'' species}}
{{As of|2014|June}} ''[[The Plant List]]'' recognises about 266 accepted [[Taxon|taxa]] (of species and infraspecific names) in the plant genus ''[[Scleria]]''.<ref name=TPL1/>

==Species==
This list is compiled from ''[[The Plant List]]'',<ref name=TPL2/> ''[[Germplasm Resources Information Network]]'',<ref name=GRIN/> [[Integrated Taxonomic Information System]]<ref name=ITIS/> and ''[[Flora of China (series)|Flora of China]]''.<ref name=FOC/>

